nodes.text: A number of Ishi Tib ornaments adorned the interior of Jabba's sail barge, the Khetanna and his palace on Tatooine.

These statuettes of Ishi Tib heads were first seen in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, in which they appeared adorning the interior of Jabba the Hutt's personal sail barge the Khetanna as well as his palace walls.
